==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trigeminal
<hw>Tri*gem"i*nal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Trigeminous</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Of, pertaining to,
or designating, the fifth pair of cranial nerves, which divide on each
side of the head into three main branches distributed to the orbits,
jaws, and parts of the mouth; trifacial.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trigeminous</ent>⟦br⟧
